productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Macau and I bought one.
heard about this on gypsy jazz radio, decided to give it a try.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
My co-worker Mitchell has one of these. He says it looks dry.
My co-worker Namon has one of these. He says it looks funny-looking.
